## Git Workflow

- Branch naming: `feature/<ticket-id>-short-description`, `fix/<ticket-id>-short-description`
- Commit message format: `<type>(<scope>): <description>` (Conventional Commits)
  - Types: `feat`, `fix`, `docs`, `refactor`, `test`, `chore`
  - Example: `feat(foos): add POST /foos endpoint`
- One feature per branch, small focused commits
- Always update `openspec/specs/api-spec.yml` when endpoints change
- Always update `openspec/specs/data-model.md` when DynamoDB schema changes
